2026-06-25 - V3.3.18 - Web tests: configurable curl timeout via STest::$WebTest_TIMEOUT (default 15s). Set it in a test (e.g. "; STest::$WebTest_TIMEOUT = 5;") to override the connect/transfer timeout for all following GET/POST/JSONPOST requests.
2026-06-22 - V3.3.17 - Suppress PHP 8.5's no-op ReflectionMethod::setAccessible() deprecation during test eval, preserving project error handlers; update framework wording to PHP 8.5.
2026-06-22 - V3.3.16 - Clarify stest-all executable-only default and add --all to include non-executable .stest files for listing and execution.
2026-06-22 - V3.3.15 - Fix stest/stest-all exit status handling so failed tests return non-zero for CI/cron/parallel while --generate remains successful; add stest-all --recent and --new filters.
2026-06-17 - V3.3.14 - Normal runs now auto-heal formatting-only result mismatches: when a stored result differs from the generated one only in spacing/key-order (same value), the test is re-run in "soft-regen" mode that canonicalizes just those lines and saves (reported as "reformat: N"). Real value changes stay failures. "-g" (full regen) is unchanged. NOTE: the soft-regen re-run re-executes the test (incl. web requests).
2026-06-17 - V3.3.13 - Update CLAUDE.md guidance (doc references, web-test server, stest-init, corrected internals)
2026-03-31 - V3.3.12 - Allow trailing semicolons in "~ ..." custom result syntax
